{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, you didn't fly in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they stayed in the area and announced themselves that they would like to call on a customer, a private customer, privately.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Made a social call-- it was practically a social call, with gloves and spats and-- and-- and-- and a hat, and so on-- and were received in a social way.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then presented their-- well, it was almost like a menu, their-- their-- their-- their-- their their card of what they had to offer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the customer would order by the-- by the case of-- of wine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, of course, if it was an established customer, they would trust the taste of the business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If not, maybe they knew somebody else who was an established customer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he had a steady clientele.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he was away for, oh, three, four, five weeks at a go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because they would travel to East Prussia, and-- my grandfather did this too-- and sell there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they would be in touch by phone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Every Friday night, they both called up, and-- because we were together with my grandparents, and-- and, you know, we were all together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we all got on the phone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it wasn't that far in the dark ages that there was no phone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But he-- it was a sort of a-- a gentlemanly profession.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he got along with all these people who were, oh, landed gentry and what have you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But also, doctors and lawyers and so on-- people who love to drink wine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they moved to-- after the war, after the First World War, when his two brothers were killed, my grandparents didn't want to stay where they were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were too many memories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they moved to Mainz, where they had a lot of relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
